---
title: Homestyle Beef Cottage Pie with Cheesy Potato Mash Topping
description: This classic comfort dish is the perfect way to warm up. Imagine a hearty hug on a plate, with a rich, meaty filling topped and a
fluffy blanket of cheesy mashed potatoes. Happiness is just a bite away!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/6735a3f646194b512b4078f0-4cd200a7.jpeg
